prodNameC: 〝鐳定〞胰島素前質 C-胜呔放射免疫分析試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
1.I125 C-peptide：11mL, contains I125 labeled C-peptide in phosphate buffer with bovine serum album in and sodium azide.
2.C-Peptide Calibrators：CAL 1-6：1mL each；CAL0：2mL.
3.C-Peptide Antiserum：10mL, contains lyophilized sheep anti C-peptide in phosphate buffer with bovine serum albumin and sodium azide.
4.C-Peptide Diluent：12.5mL, contains lyophilized bovine gammaglobulins, bovine serum albumin and sodium azide.
5.Serotest M：1mL, Containing human serum, freeze-dried with sodium azide.
6.20% TW PEG Solution：125mL.
